==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Byzantium
<hw>Byzantium</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>An ancient city on the
Bosphorus founded by the Greeks. It was later renamed
<altname>Constaninople</altname> in honor of the emperor
<persfn>Constantine</persfn>, and renamed <altname>Istanbul</altname> by
the Turks, which name it still retains.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

